            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThe%20prophet%20Jeremiah%20could%20foresee%20Jesus'%20first%20coming.%20Though%20he%20lived%20hundreds%20of%20years%20before%20Christ's%20birth%2C%20Jeremiah%20saw%20by%20the%20Spirit%20of%20God%20that%20One%20was%20coming%20from%20the%20line%20of%20David%20who%20would%20blaze%20a%20trail%20that%20would%20ultimately%20touch%20every%20person%20in%20history.%20He%20would%20restore%20total%20justice%20and%20wisdom%20to%20a%20sin-gripped%20land.%20Jeremiah%20saw%20a%20time%20when%20Judah%20would%20be%20saved%2C%20and%20Israel%20would%20live%20in%20safety.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20name%20of%20the%20One%20who%20would%20accomplish%20this%3A%20The%20Lord%20Is%20Our%20Righteousness.%20What%20name%20could%20better%20describe%20Jesus%3F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPaul%20saw%20ahead%20in%20time%20to%20the%20second%20coming%20of%20Jesus.%20He%20saw%20the%20Lord%20coming%20back%20from%20heaven%20%22with%20his%20mighty%20angels%2C%20in%20flaming%20fire%22%20(2%20Thessalonians%201%3A7-8).%20Like%20Jeremiah%2C%20he%20saw%20ahead%20to%20the%20time%20when%20Jesus%20will%20set%20everything%20right%20on%20earth%20again-a%20time%20when%20He%20will%20eternally%20punish%20the%20wicked%20and%20they%20will%20be%20%22forever%20separated%20from%20the%20Lord%20and%20from%20his%20glorious%20power%22%20(v.%209).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20Jesus%20returns%2C%20He%20will%20assume%20all%20the%20glory%20on%20earth%20and%20be%20worshiped%20by%20both%20the%20Church%20and%20the%20Jewish%20converts.%20%22In%20that%20day%20Judah%20will%20be%20saved%2C%20and%20Israel%20will%20live%20in%20safety%22%20(Jeremiah%2023%3A6).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGet%20ready%20and%20stay%20ready%2C%20for%20The%20Lord%20Our%20Righteousness%20is%20on%20His%20way.%20He's%20coming%20for%20you!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
